# Supabase / database

Full schema: `docs/DATABASE.md`. Migrations in `supabase/migrations/` — never edit applied migrations.

- RLS on every table from day one; `authenticated` required
- Imports: store `source_raw` + `source_hash` on `play_sessions`; idempotent upserts
- `session_messages` replaces v1 JSONB chat on board_games
- Trigger: create `profiles` row on `auth.users` insert

After schema changes: regenerate types (`pnpm db:types` when script exists).
